  "title": "OFFICE HOURS 5.5 DAYS TEMP PHARMACY TECHNICIAN NEEDED!! ($20/H) #HCGT",
  "description": "<p><strong>Role Overview</strong></p><ul><li><p>Prepare and dispense medications to polyclinic patients in line with prescribed instructions</p></li><li><p>Support medication distribution through delivery services and PILBOX collection points</p></li><li><p>Provide remote dispensing services when applicable</p></li><li><p>Assist in video consultations and carry out medication reconciliation</p></li><li><p>Willing to travel and work across multiple locations as required</p></li></ul><p><strong>Qualifications</strong></p><ul><li><p>GCE ‘O’ Level with recognised training as a Pharmacy Technician (MOH/PSS accredited or equivalent), or a Diploma in Pharmaceutical Science</p></li><li><p>Open to fresh diploma graduates as well as candidates with relevant pharmacy technician experience<br /><br />All qualified\napplicants, please send in your resume to:</p><p><a href=\"mailto:medicalhealth@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">medicalhealth@recruitexpress.com.sg</a></p><p>Tricia Celestine Goh (R1981653)<br />\nRecruit Express Pte Ltd | Company Reg. No.\n199601303W | EA License Number: 99C4599</p></li></ul>",
